{"tid":845671,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓爆加價】上源加推310伙周六發售 較首批貴4%","createTime":"2018-10-03T00:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T02:07:30.000Z","uid":43146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c63fd058244604327d47ab34d08543718644e56","tid":845671,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T00:19:39.000Z","msg":"內房萬科(香港)屯門掃管笏上源繼昨日沽清347伙單位，套現約21億元後，今日加推310伙單位，以定價計市值約25億元，單位折實呎價1.15萬元，較首張價單折實均價11,073元略貴3.86%，該批單位將於本周六(6日)出售。<br />\n<br />\n發展商表示，該批單位提供36伙1房戶，184伙2房戶及90伙3房戶，實用面積由335至829方呎，扣除16%折扣優惠及1%回贈後，折實售價由456.48萬至990.49萬元，當中約16伙折實價低於500萬元；入場單位為T6B座1樓F單位，實用394方呎，折實價456.5萬元，折實呎價11,586元。<br />\n<br />\n全球樓行 Dream House零距離<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&d=iUr0gEzqSs0uuOOQL8Ar1HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=83ecaea4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&h=9bc132df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181002/58747211\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181002%2F58747211&d=iUr0gEzqSs0uuOOQL8Ar1HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ea9f4c18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181002%2F58747211&h=3b142631\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181002/58747211</a>"},{"pid":"c21fe6ff22b83aaee6eca6637311ccbef0971b60","tid":845671,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}